    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该游戏是一款简单的2D动作游戏，带有Roguelite元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你正在某个房间里玩游戏。如果你能在躲避周围冲来的敌人的情况下生存5分钟，你就通关了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297030/extras/b2af6b2fb53d01d60d0c3e4655944bd4.avif?t=1741282436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297030/extras_big/b2af6b2fb53d01d60d0c3e4655944bd4.avif?t=1741282436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一开始你可能会发现很难选择技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297030/extras/a1ce10251342696a511be460bd11daed.avif?t=1741282436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297030/extras_big/a1ce10251342696a511be460bd11daed.avif?t=1741282436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您发现游戏难以通关，我们建议您停止游戏并休息一下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次开始游戏都会有新的发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我相信您会认出这个房间的本来面目。</p>",
